name: Vessels 176: The Stronghold
description:
In another life Stronghold could have been a brilliant cop and a force for justice.  Things have not gone that way for him in the colony though...  Through a series of circumstances mostly out of his control, Stronghold has ended up a very bad man indeed.  Deep behind those cold (glowing!) blue eyes there still may be some good...

His crimes are too long to list but he has gold in his pocket and blood on his fists.

Wanted by the queens guard, he has several bounties on his head but there are few with the courage to try to claim his and the trail of bodies left in his wake act as a strong deterrent.
